    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "The Partnership provides consolidated support for: two previously funded agreements with the UN Peace Building Commission (PBC, Peace Building Fund (PBF) and UNICEF's Monitoring and Reporting Mechanism; two previously approved no-costs extensions with the UN Rule of Law Index (ROLIX) and the Department of Political Affairs (DPA); and provision of new funding to the Bureau of Crisis Prevention and Recovery. This initiative supports UN program work in fragile and conflict-affected countries. The total value of this multi-country initiative is $35.9 million over 7 years, starting 2009-10."
      },
